                "invention-title": [
                    "System for preparing reduced iron through short-process continuous hydrogen reduction",
                    "一种短流程连续氢还原制备还原铁的系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a system for preparing reduced iron through short-process continuous hydrogen reduction. The system comprises a dehydration and dechlorination assembly, a reduction assembly, a cooling assembly, a condensation and concentration assembly and a controller. The dehydration and dechlorination assembly comprises a barrel, a stranding cage spiral conveyor is arranged in the barrel, and an electromagnetic heating coil is arranged on the outer side of the barrel; the cooling assembly comprises a cooling section cylinder and a cooling section sealing feeder; the condensation and concentration assembly comprises a spiral pipe, a gas-water separator, a gas dryer and a gas pressurization Roots blower which are connected in sequence; the spiral pipe is connected with a reduction section cylinder at the right end of the reduction section sealing feeder through a pipeline; the gas pressurized Roots blower is connected with a cooling section cylinder at the right end of the cooling section sealing feeder through a pipeline; and a condensation and concentration section condensation pipe is arranged outside the spiral pipe. The elemental iron is prepared through three-stage dechlorination and dehydration, reduction and cooling, heat conduction is enhanced through electromagnetic heating, and energy consumption is effectively reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种短流程连续氢还原制备还原铁的系统，包括脱水除氯组件、还原组件、冷却组件、冷凝浓缩组件、控制器；脱水除氯组件包括筒体，筒体内部设有绞笼螺旋输送机，筒体外侧设有电磁加热线圈；冷却组件包括冷却段筒体、冷却段密封给料器；冷凝浓缩组件包括依次相连的螺旋管、气水分离器、气体干燥器、气体加压罗茨风；螺旋管通过管路与还原段密封给料器右端的还原段筒体连接；气体加压罗茨风通过管路与冷却段密封给料器右端的冷却段筒体连接；螺旋管外部设有冷凝浓缩段冷凝管。本发明采用三段式脱氯脱水、还原、冷却进行单质铁的制备，利用电磁加热强化热传导，有效降低能耗。"
                }
